It's hard to describe @specialneedsnetwork #PinkPumpGala Its a must attend gala for LA female power players; it's an emotional and heart wrenching afternoon with friends; it's a fashion extravaganza; its an opportunity to rock the pink; it's an event to raise hundreds of thousands of dollars for the only free Autism summer camp in S CA; and most of all, it's a gathering of powerful women that know that they can change the world, one child at a time! That's why on #girlcrushwednesday I'm proud to post a pic from #PinkPump 2015 with me wearing an @eduardolucerola original! It was Vegas themed baby and we were betting on our kids' future! This year's gala is SOLD OUT thanks to 300 amazing women and a few good men! #PinkPump #PinkPump2017 #gala #autism #fashion #pumps #pink
